  "title": "Maintenance Technician (Training Provided)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic $2000 to $3500 + AWS + VB</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working location: Hougang / Site (Island Wide)</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>5 days’ work week (8:30am to 5:30pm)</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Communications equipment (Radio; Network; Wireless)</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Training Provided</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Carry out daily preventive maintenance and corrective maintenance of Radio, Network and Wireless equipment at site, including inspection, troubleshooting and replacement of faulty equipment</strong></li>\n  <li>Run tests and interpret results to ensure equipment is operating functionally</li>\n  <li><strong>Assist engineer in-charge to supervise site works</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Communicate with customers and various stakeholders of the project</strong></li>\n  <li>Supervise subcontractors for site works</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>NITEC and/or Diploma in Electrical / Electronic Engineering or equivalent</li>\n  <li><strong>Candidate without experience is welcome as Training will be provided</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now</strong> button with the following information in the resume</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>NG DIAUM YEE (R2198031)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
